PrecisEnactment of the EXEMPTION FROM THE APPLICATION OF SUBSECTION 103(1) OF THE CUSTOMS TARIFF REGULATIONS which set out the time limits and the circumstances under which goods that are diverted for use in an emergency or destroyed prior to exportation are exempted from the reporting and repayment requirements of subsection 103(1) of the Customs Tariff.
